{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"## WS7 + WS6-b COMPLETE — Gerrit-only cutover verified end-to-end (2026-07-01)\n\nExecuted prove-then-lock (user-approved), main-only lock (tags left open for releases).\n\n### Deliverables\n- **CONTRIBUTING.md** (new) — full Gerrit contributor flow; **CLAUDE.md** git-workflow section\n  rewritten (agents push refs/for/main, not GitHub PRs); README links both. LANDED THROUGH GERRIT\n  as change 121 (dogfood), not a GitHub PR.\n- **Gerrit main seeded** to GitHub main (was 40+1 commits behind; temp admin-push grant → FF →\n  revoked; gate restored to pure review-only). Re-seeded after PR #115 landed (per user).\n- **GitHub main locked**: created ruleset `gerrit-mirror-lock-main` (id 18402431, deploy-key-only\n  `update`+`deletion`+`non_fast_forward`, bypass = DeployKey always); deleted legacy `main-protection`\n  (18306946; snapshot saved for rollback). Tags left OPEN (release.yml v* pushes keep working).\n- Gerrit project default branch set master → main.\n\n### Proof (WS6-b dogfood)\n- change 121: pushed to refs/for/main → review-bot cast LLM-Review over 4 patchsets (findings\n  addressed each round; votes correctly dropped on real code changes, re-applied) → +1, 0 unresolved\n  → submitted → merged to Gerrit main (a6f690de).\n- Replication: FAILED pre-lock (\"push declined due to repository rule violations\" — legacy ruleset\n  blocked the deploy key), SUCCEEDED post-lock → GitHub main advanced to a6f690de (CONTRIBUTING.md\n  landed on the mirror as the first Gerrit-replicated change).\n- Lock verified: a clean fast-forward human push to GitHub main is REJECTED (\"GH013: Cannot update\n  this protected ref\"); only the replication deploy key can advance main.\n\n### Operational facts / follow-ups\n- Break-glass admin: session SSH key at /root/.ssh/gerrit_admin on the box (root-only); admin\n  account 1000000 has no HTTP password (SSH-only). JoeOakhartNava (1000007) is admin + has an HTTP pw.\n- Rollback: snapshot at $CLAUDE_JOB_DIR/tmp/legacy-ruleset-18306946.json; re-create legacy or add an\n  admin bypass to unlock.\n- Deferred (WS7 plan-review advisories, non-blocking): Terraform-github state reconcile + drift\n  detection (adv 2,9,15), replication-health + ruleset-drift alerting (adv 5,6). Creating\n  discovered_from tickets."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782943572774449001,"uuid":"a2a0d09d-bb1e-478e-bdbe-1d52050179cb"}